The '''Kalaanite resistance''' was an organization of [[Kalaanite]]s fighting the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. [[Kalaan/Legends|Kalaan]] had been a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] world prior to the [[Battle of Kalaan]], in which the Empire pushed the Alliance off the planet and destroyed [[Kalaan City]]. The Kalaanite resistance continued to attack Imperial forces. The Empire ravaged much of Kalaan, completely denuding it of flora. Most resistance fighters were light infantry which fought as guerrillas, but heavier infantry existed. The Kalaanites also managed to capture multiple [[All Terrain Scout Transport/Legends|AT-STs]], which they were able to turn against the Empire. In [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], several resistance fighters [[Escape from Kalaan|aided]] [[Brenn Tantor]] in defecting, helping him and [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] cross Kalaan's hills and reach [[Tyr Taskeen]]'s Rebel base, which was in the process of evacuating.

